Docker compose: 

Docker compose is a tool manages containers. It used for defining and running multi container docker applications in a single YAML file 

Docker compose commands:
 To run the docker-compose file 
- 'docker-compose up'
to remove all the containers
- 'docker-compose down'
- docker-compose build
- docker-compose logs
- docker-compose ps
- docker-compose version
- docker-compose port
- docker-compose top
- docker-compose kill
- docker-compose pause
- docker-compose unpause
- docker-compose rm
- docker-compose exec
- docker-compose run
- docker-compose pull